songs.title: Christmas [Baby Please Come Home] (Cover)
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1: Lauren]
They're singing "Deck The Halls"
But it's not like Christmas at all
Cause I remember when you were here
And all the fun we had last year

[Chorus: Camila & All]
Christmas
The snow's coming down
Christmas
I'm watching it fall
Christmas
Lots of people around
Christmas
Baby please come home
Christmas
The church bells in town
Christmas
All ringing in song
Christmas
Full of happy sounds
Christmas
Baby please come home

[Verse 2: Normani]
They're singing "Deck The Halls"
But it's not like Christmas at all
Cause I remember when you were here
And all the fun we had last year

[Chorus: Ally & All]
Christmas
If there was a way
Christmas
I'd hold back this tear
Christmas
But it's Christmas day
Christmas
Baby please come home

[Verse 2: Dinah]
They're singing "Deck The Halls"
But it's not like Christmas at all
I remember when you were here
And all the fun we had last year

[Chorus: Dinah & All]
Christmas
I want you warm
Christmas
I'm hoping you come
Christmas
And all the children out here
Christmas
Please please please please, baby please come home
Christmas
Baby please come home
Christmas
